As far as 'country-club' syndrome for the IGB, I don't buy it.  You don't get into the NFL with Biloxi Baywatchers, you don't get into the NBA with Hoboken Hooters, what makes you think that something equivalent in EQ would be any easier?  It has nothing to do with trying to shut smaller guilds out, in fact, it's very much the opposite.  If it was there to shut you out,  Druzzil would be an absolute pit.<br>
